{"tid":2107794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家鼓勵同支持番初選落選的手足們，勇敢企出黎選係一啲都唔容易","createTime":"2020-07-14T06:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T06:39:43.000Z","uid":108201,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"279bf2fd7b9a32035dbf3fe18de84754405dd712","tid":2107794,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再互相批評願意出黎初選的手足們啦，其實佢哋走出黎選係一d都唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算民主黨，公民黨過去有幾多不足，如果佢哋唔選初選，其實每區都可以會有立法會一席，佢哋都願意放下包袱一齊選，輸左都係值得我哋尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋面對極權，係無再分裂的本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家鼓勵番落選的手足們，繼續同我哋走依條漫長而黑暗的光復香港之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我係受我尋晚發的post，各位巴打願意鼓勵安德里所感動，有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人都心底尊重安德里？有無興趣去重慶大廈比番鼓勵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2107012\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2107012</a>"},{"pid":"52fbc8fc3c89ad106506bd0b5f2bef5b32d0282d","tid":2107794,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878f46346c74e05e961ff3633ae88e8d8b510981","tid":2107794,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"希望大家鼓勵番各位落選手足們，互相支持係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想起上年818的一張相，努力走落去係唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3FUN2cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?